name: Catty Wants Some Milk
description:
Welcome to the forest!

There is a greedy cat name Catty.  Long ago, a man from the human town came to the forest and feed her with milk. She can't forget that delicious taste and plans to go to the human town to find more milk.

I hope you can enjoy this game!

Control

W, A, S, D to move.

Walk towards others and talk to them. You need their help.

Walk on the items to pick them up.
